title: The OC Savior: Ep. 9, Total Bullsh*t
itunes:title: The OC Savior: Ep. 9, Total Bullsh*t
description:
Queen of the Con host Johathan Walton has uncovered new evidence that proves... while Lizzie Mulder was pleading guilty to scamming more than a dozen people in Orange County out of $1.5 million, she was also scamming a federal judge and two federal prosecutors. They just had no idea. But now that they know - will Lizzie Mulder face any consequences?
